com.datastax.dse.driver.api.core.metadata.schema

Interface DseGraphKeyspaceMetadata

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Describable, DseKeyspaceMetadata, KeyspaceMetadata

    public interface DseGraphKeyspaceMetadata
extends DseKeyspaceMetadata
    Specialized keyspace metadata, that handles the graph-specific properties introduced in DSE 6.8.

    This type only exists to avoid breaking binary compatibility. When the driver is connected to a DSE cluster, all the KeyspaceMetadata instances it returns can be safely downcast to this interface.
